config

Class LoopConfigDefault

  • java.lang.Object
    • config.LoopConfigDefault

  • public abstract class LoopConfigDefault
extends java.lang.Object
    Class used to pass into Looper as a config. Create a new class that extends from this one and use the abstract setConfig() method to set all variables that you need to change. Any not set in that method will use the default value set here.
    Author:
    Trevor
